title: Healthy Together - COVID-19
description: Healthy Together is made in partnership with the Florida Department of Health for residents of Florida to help stop the spread of COVID-19. Healthy Together's mission is to improve the collective health of our community. Our platform enables the future of public health through next-generation technology that empowers public health institutions and residents. Healthy Together's mobile application helps Florida citizens: - Get real time, in-app COVID-19 test results - Complete digital contact tracing interviews when positive for COVID-19 - Get public health announcements through the Notification Center User Data, Privacy & Security - There is no mandate to participate in this effort, users choose to opt-in. - Users are in full control of their personal data. They decide what they share and can reverse those decisions as well as delete their data at any time. - All symptom data is automatically de-identified after 30-days. - Data is encrypted in transit and at rest. The use of this data is limited to COVID-19 response efforts, public health & research purposes. View our full Privacy Policy at www.healthytogether.io/legal/privacy
